{"tid":1280211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"興民邨女子被非法禁錮強姦 警拘3男女","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T02:16:39.000Z","uid":53003,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bc89588566e6565f357f5592242686e1187e5515","tid":1280211,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190702/59782878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190702%2F59782878&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=12f17a8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190702%2F59782878&h=c583a7b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190702/59782878</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190702/large/1562080272_9730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190702%2Flarge%2F1562080272_9730.jpg&h=9b68238f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕3名男女。姜偉康攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190702/large/1562080272_4bcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190702%2Flarge%2F1562080272_4bcb.jpg&h=6a909649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員區諾軒與區議員黎志強到場了解事件。姜偉康攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190702/large/1562079688_3c8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190702%2Flarge%2F1562079688_3c8a.jpg&h=2fafba04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多名警員手持盾牌到興民邨調查。香港突發事故報料區圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190702/large/1562080272_9a64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190702%2Flarge%2F1562080272_9a64.jpg&h=e1bf9e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名女子需要送院檢查。姜偉康攝<br />\n<br />\n柴灣發生非法禁錮及強姦案！晚上7時許，警方接獲報案，指有人被非法禁錮在興民邨一單位，多名警員手持盾牌到場調查，氣氛緊張，其間更有人在上址一單位內與警員對峙。<br />\n<br />\n事件大約擾攘一小時後，警方終拘捕屋內兩名34及25歲男子及一名28歲女子，而另一名42歲女子需要送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，相信女事主在上址單位被人非法禁錮及強姦，三名男女涉案被捕。案件交由東區警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n有關相片及片段被人上載至fb群組，發帖者聲稱「大批差佬喺興民邨check學生」，事件引來一眾網民熱烈討論，擔心有示威者遭警圍捕，惟立法會議員區諾軒到場了解後，證實事件屬非法禁錮。區議員黎志強引述警民關係組表示，與立法會的事情無關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190702/large/1562081411_b61e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190702%2Flarge%2F1562081411_b61e.jpg&h=d59fa5ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd62c56b5e5467e6ef6326f91661476478ef274d","tid":1280211,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:49:44.000Z","msg":"大家記緊冷靜返啲先，記得fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4914c6fc76d174629a8412d84b650c3bb794b7","tid":1280211,"uid":198900,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"42歲都被人老強？屌老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff381cdf8e29ca338283c83d410d6404d3cc82b9","tid":1280211,"uid":68902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f4914c6fc76d174629a8412d84b650c3bb794b7","tid":1280211,"uid":198900,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"42歲都被人老強？屌老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:58:24.000Z","msg":"熟女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58ab6101a927eb8514c4a062a522e95e64cb044","tid":1280211,"uid":14103,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"34歲同25歲男子 夾埋一個28歲女子去姦一個45歲老人？"},{"pid":"398e228ebee0e9c31fdae7decd620f0947be3eaf","tid":1280211,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"屌 嚇撚死我"},{"pid":"65281882c32a1cd97f62bd61b643510575b8c818","tid":1280211,"uid":237425,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:05:55.000Z","msg":"２８歲都仲講得通<br />\n４２咩料呀"},{"pid":"0545951b1f1ed773daf2c3cce46e369dfeb6800a","tid":1280211,"uid":86756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:08:59.000Z","msg":"冇人站在42歲老女人嘅立場，佢比人女女女咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f113e22d9eb186ffa02160dca4b4f3c78354140","tid":1280211,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"28戱女唔好過42歲女？重口味"},{"pid":"6db3931add2b8d4d7c3f742967227c18b7ee0413","tid":1280211,"uid":263235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f4914c6fc76d174629a8412d84b650c3bb794b7","tid":1280211,"uid":198900,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"42歲都被人老強？屌老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"特別口味"},{"pid":"3d7cf2cec01e4bd8d726fccf77d92721de9d0aa1","tid":1280211,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:10:43.000Z","msg":"42歲啫<br />\n可能細細粒咁嘅樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e98658dc9890b369afc94d443ae470d731513ae","tid":1280211,"uid":47643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"41歲得唔得?<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/05/20190504-EN-%E6%9E%97%E5%98%89%E6%AC%A32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F05%2F20190504-EN-%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%2598%2589%25E6%25AC%25A32.jpg&h=f3dbf615&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}